{"title":"DFS深度优先搜索技术","uid":"2bdbc871dc8d9490d9e90b4615d9268f","slug":"DFS深度优先搜索技术","date":"2026-01-25T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2026-01-22T13:56:01.217Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/DFS深度优先搜索技术.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>DFS是一种算法技术，一般通过DFS函数来实现其功能。</p>\n<h1 id=\"DFS函数的内容\"><a href=\"#DFS函数的内容\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"DFS函数的内容\"></a>DFS函数的内容</h1><p>1，终止条件<br>2，标记已访问节点<br>3，访问下一层节点，<strong>通常该步骤包含DFS函数的递归，且访问完应该注意节点状态更新</strong><br>4，回溯当前节点</p>\n<h1 id=\"模板\"><a href=\"#模板\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"模板\"></a>模板</h1><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">/**</span><br><span class=\"line\"> * 标准 DFS 函数模板</span><br><span class=\"line\"> * @param node     当前访问的节点（或当前状态）</span><br><span class=\"line\"> * @param G        图的邻接表</span><br><span class=\"line\"> * @param visited  访问标记数组</span><br><span class=\"line\"> */</span><br><span class=\"line\">void dfs(int node, vector&lt;vector&lt;int&gt;&gt;&amp; G, vector&lt;bool&gt;&amp; visited) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    // 1. 终止条件 / 基础处理</span><br><span class=\"line\">    // (如果是处理树结构，通常在这里判断 node == nullptr)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    // 2. 标记当前节点已访问</span><br><span class=\"line\">    visited[node] = true;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    cout &lt;&lt; &quot;访问节点: &quot; &lt;&lt; node &lt;&lt; endl; </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    // 3. 遍历邻居节点（选择列表）</span><br><span class=\"line\">    for (int neighbor : G[node]) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        </span><br><span class=\"line\">        // 4. 合法性检查与递归</span><br><span class=\"line\">        if (!visited[neighbor]) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            </span><br><span class=\"line\">            // 递归进入下一层</span><br><span class=\"line\">            dfs(neighbor, G, visited);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            </span><br><span class=\"line\">            // 5. 回溯 (Backtracking) - 可选</span><br><span class=\"line\">            /* 如果是求所有路径或排列组合，</span><br><span class=\"line\">               通常在这里执行 visited[neighbor] = false; </span><br><span class=\"line\">            */</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","feature":true,"text":"DFS是一种算法技术，一般通过DFS函数来实现其功能。 DFS函数的内容1，终止条件2，标记已访问节点3，访问下一层节点，通常该步骤包含DFS函数的递归，且访问...","permalink":"/post/DFS深度优先搜索技术","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":911,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"算法 - DFS","slug":"算法-DFS","count":1,"path":"api/categories/算法-DFS.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"DFS","slug":"DFS","count":2,"path":"api/tags/DFS.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#DFS%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%8